Text:
Excellent Download.  
This is the latest "beta" of 1.6.5 Mac OSX.

Downloaded from User_1 before.  Quality stuff.  
Thank you User_1

Be very careful on the Combo. The only Combo I am aware that's floating around at this point is a machine specific package and this can ruin your Mac OS X. There's been various states of damage being reported on MacRumors.com. Wait for the official Apple Combo package!

If you really want to try it, then be warned to use it on a spare OS installation, one that won't harm your critical data.
